title: Garden Landscapes
description:
Garden Landscapes by Sophia Song, Marcelo Novas

Overview: The book is edited by Brazilian designer Marcelo Novas. He carefully displays more than 20 works in the book. Readers can feel the charm of real art in this book.

Surprising, enchanting, highly sophisticated... This is a book that takes you on a tour of Brazil s most beautiful gardens, unveiling the refinement of very special projects and the oeuvre of one of the greatest contemporary landscape architects
